{"type": "article", "id": 22748, "title": "方形水瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-24T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 143, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125957lnCecZXU4LBb93Eg.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个水瓶，有点像一瓶香水。采用透明的不含 BPA 的塑料制作，表面没有彩色的图样，近似长方体的外形自有一种干净和精致，它同样也适合夹在书中。设计者来自澳大利亚，他们忧心于人们对水瓶的浪费而设计了这款瓶子，A5、A6 分别可容纳 750ml、375ml ，后者可以直接装在口袋里。有黑色或白色两种盖子选择，售价 22 澳元起，<a href=\"http://www.memobottle.com/pages/thememobottlestory\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125953pLmN3T8vSVHe6k4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125954dcA5UFCJzO7Lo4Pw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125954YLakq2lFB6s4XKGp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125955bg7u95DTUEmihG63.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125956qfD1tsPHXRE9Uz2k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125956aSuKACk9137Yjipd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}